{"tid":613761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花貓倒斃深水埗路邊 愛協到場調查","createTime":"2018-04-02T03:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T06:08:07.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75767e7b0643fa4b5ed2dc2724601e66289f54fd","tid":613761,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180402/large/1522639448_9a8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180402%2Flarge%2F1522639448_9a8c.jpg&h=d7a73ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貓隻已死去一段時間，死因有待進一步了解。(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n早上9時46分，有途人在深水埗黃竹街25號對開馬路，發現一隻花貓屍體，懷疑遭虐殺，於是報警。警方到場，用紙盒將貓屍遮蓋，並通知愛護動物協會人員協助，初步調查顯示，貓隻已死去一段時間，死因有待進一步了解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180402/58024276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F58024276&d=hk8iL1Q5AFeEi9VmpvWFnr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=220c34b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F58024276&h=6baf7dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180402/58024276</a>"},{"pid":"5b2a75bf3ff755a429a6cc5e57d5efd8252c355a","tid":613761,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"咁都有新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271800af86a8b9d7b4487bcf10ea34268bc8d82b","tid":613761,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b2a75bf3ff755a429a6cc5e57d5efd8252c355a","tid":613761,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"咁都有新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"虐殺喎<img src=\"/a